stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR
  [*] --> OpenPending: 设计人员创建批注<br/>resolutionStatus=open<br/>decisionStatus=pending

  OpenPending --> FixedPending: 设计标记 fixed<br/>resolutionStatus=fixed
  OpenPending --> WontFixPending: 设计标记 wont_fix<br/>resolutionStatus=wont_fix

  FixedPending --> FixedAgreed: 校对/审核 agree
  FixedPending --> FixedRejected: 校对/审核 reject
  WontFixPending --> WontFixAgreed: 校对/审核 agree
  WontFixPending --> WontFixRejected: 校对/审核 reject

  FixedRejected --> OpenPending: 设计重新处理
  WontFixRejected --> OpenPending: 设计重新处理

  FixedAgreed --> [*]
  WontFixAgreed --> [*]

  note right of OpenPending
    action=fixed/wont_fix 由设计
    action=agree/reject 由校对/审核
    严重度独立存储:
    suggestion/normal/severe/critical
  end note
